TITLE: Using the TestDox attribute in PHP for PHPUnit
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to use the TestDox attribute to customize the text printed for a test when TestDox output is enabled. This attribute can be used at both class and method levels and is not repeatable.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sebastianbergmann/phpunit-documentation-english/blob/12.0/src/attributes.rst#2025-04-23_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
<?php declare(strict_types=1);
use PHPUnit\Framework\Attributes\TestDox;
use PHPUnit\Framework\TestCase;

