TITLE: Using assertThat() with Constraints in PHP with PHPUnit
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use assertThat() with logicalNot() and equalTo() constraints to create more complex assertions in PHPUnit. This example shows a test that is equivalent to using assertNotEquals() to verify that a biscuit is not made of chocolate.
