TITLE: PHPUnit Configuration in Phive's phars.xml
DESCRIPTION: XML configuration that Phive generates to track PHPUnit as a project dependency with version constraints.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sebastianbergmann/phpunit-documentation-english/blob/12.0/src/installation.rst#2025-04-23_snippet_18

LANGUAGE: xml
CODE:
```
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<phive xmlns="https://phar.io/phive">
  <phar name="phpunit"
        version="^10.0" installed="10.0.0"
        location="./tools/phpunit" copy="true"/>
</phive>
```

