TITLE: PHP Development Configuration Settings
DESCRIPTION: PHP configuration directives for development environment, including error reporting, assertion handling, and memory settings.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sebastianbergmann/phpunit-documentation-english/blob/12.0/src/installation.rst#2025-04-23_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
error_reporting=-1

xdebug.show_exception_trace=0

xdebug.mode=coverage

zend.assertions=1
assert.exception=1

memory_limit=-1
```

